description:
This week we're joined by Danielle and her college best friend, Delaney Free! The two talk about Grammy nominations, their current favorite products, how they met, what it's like being friends with Danielle, their plans to live together next year, dating in college, how Delaney got into modeling, and oh so much more - enjoy!
